{"words":[{"word":"paranormal","count":4},{"word":"something","count":3},{"word":"dark","count":3},{"word":"side","count":3},{"word":"playername","count":2},{"word":"already","count":2},{"word":"fan","count":2},{"word":"club","count":2},{"word":"first","count":2},{"word":"guessing","count":2},{"word":"into","count":2},{"word":"unknown","count":2},{"word":"girl","count":1},{"word":"caselli","count":1},{"word":"happened","count":1},{"word":"told","count":1},{"word":"dorky","count":1},{"word":"hobby","count":1},{"word":"group","count":1},{"word":"strange","count":1},{"word":"happens","count":1},{"word":"hey","count":1},{"word":"curiosity's","count":1},{"word":"great","count":1},{"word":"suddenly","count":1},{"word":"prime","count":1},{"word":"suspect","count":1},{"word":"good","count":1},{"word":"lay","count":1},{"word":"next","count":1},{"word":"time","count":1},{"word":"basically","count":1},{"word":"neighborhood","count":1},{"word":"watch","count":1},{"word":"job","count":1},{"word":"without","count":1},{"word":"intelligence","count":1},{"word":"network","count":1},{"word":"yeah","count":1},{"word":"going","count":1},{"word":"trust","count":1},{"word":"secrets","count":1},{"word":"heavier","count":1},{"word":"myth","count":1},{"word":"myths","count":1},{"word":"plenty","count":1},{"word":"story","count":1},{"word":"heard","count":1},{"word":"thing's","count":1},{"word":"sure","count":1},{"word":"academy","count":1},{"word":"oversees","count":1},{"word":"investigation","count":1},{"word":"science","count":1},{"word":"different","count":1},{"word":"ways","count":1},{"word":"explain","count":1},{"word":"exists","count":1},{"word":"talk","count":1},{"word":"cowards","count":1},{"word":"unexplainable","count":1},{"word":"phenomena","count":1},{"word":"around","count":1},{"word":"gateway","count":1},{"word":"hear","count":1},{"word":"wind","count":1},{"word":"behind","count":1},{"word":"door","count":1},{"word":"welcomes","count":1},{"word":"whether","count":1},{"word":"made","count":1},{"word":"past","count":1},{"word":"layer","count":1}],"lines":[{"text":"{PlayerName}, that girl, Caselli… Something happened to her, didn't it?","quest_name":"Urban Legend: The Tale Teller","quest_id":189700017},{"text":"Told you already. Our Paranormal Fan Club isn't just some dorky hobby group. When something strange happens, we're the first to know.","quest_name":"Urban Legend: The Tale Teller","quest_id":189700017},{"text":"…Hey! Curiosity's great, but why am I suddenly the prime suspect?","quest_name":"Urban Legend: The Tale Teller","quest_id":189700017},{"text":"You're good at guessing. Just lay off guessing next time.","quest_name":"Urban Legend: The Tale Teller","quest_id":189700017},{"text":"Come on, we're basically the paranormal neighborhood watch. You think we could do our job without our own intelligence network?","quest_name":"Urban Legend: The Tale Teller","quest_id":189700017},{"text":"So yeah, I know what's going on with her. And trust me, the Dark Side has secrets way heavier than that.","quest_name":"Urban Legend: The Tale Teller","quest_id":189700017},{"text":"The Dark Side isn't a myth. But the myths about it? Plenty. I don't know which story you heard, but one thing's for sure, the Academy oversees our investigation into it.","quest_name":"Urban Legend: The Tale Teller","quest_id":189700017},{"text":"Science or the paranormal, both are just different ways to explain the unknown. If something exists, why <i>shouldn't</i> we talk about it?","quest_name":"Urban Legend: The Tale Teller","quest_id":189700017},{"text":"We're not cowards. To me, the Dark Side and all unexplainable phenomena around it are a gateway into the unknown.","quest_name":"Urban Legend: The Tale Teller","quest_id":189700017},{"text":"Hear it? The wind behind that door—","quest_name":"Urban Legend: The Tale Teller","quest_id":189700017},{"text":"The Paranormal Fan Club welcomes you, {PlayerName}. Whether you like it or not, you've already made it past the first \"layer.\"","quest_name":"Urban Legend: The Tale Teller","quest_id":189700017}]}